			description: [
				"Cu5tom Greg-E modifier, it allows machines to run 2 or more recipes in parallel. For example, you can have Steel Dust -> Steel Ingots on Thread 1, and at the same time Aluminium Dust -> Aluminium Ingots are running on Thread 2."
				""
				"Basically multiple machines in 1."
				""
				"It will still apply all the other boosts for the recipe."
			]
			id: "53E9326397CBEF52"
